022package com.restfb;
023
024import java.util.stream.Stream;
025
026public enum Version {
027
028  /**
029   * unversiond api
030   */
031  UNVERSIONED(null),
032
033  /**
034   * <tt>Graph API 3.1</tt>, available until October 23, 2020
035   *
036   * @since July 26, 2018
037   */
038  VERSION_3_1("v3.1"),
039
040  /**
041   * <tt>Graph API 3.2</tt>, available until April 30, 2021
042   *
043   * @since October 23, 2018
044   */
045  VERSION_3_2("v3.2"),
046
047  /**
048   * <tt>Graph API 3.3</tt>, available until July 29, 2021
049   *
050   * @since April 30, 2019
051   */
052  VERSION_3_3("v3.3"),
053
054  /**
055   * <tt>Graph API 4.0</tt>, available until October 29, 2021
056   *
057   * @since July 29, 2019
058   */
059  VERSION_4_0("v4.0"),
060
061  /**
062   * <tt>Graph API 5.0</tt>, available until February 3rd, 2022
063   *
064   * @since October 29, 2019
065   */
066  VERSION_5_0("v5.0"),
067
068  /**
069   * <tt>Graph API 6.0</tt>, available at least until May 5th, 2022
070   *
071   * @since February 3rd, 2020
072   */
073  VERSION_6_0("v6.0"),
074
075  /**
076   * <tt>Graph API 7.0</tt>, available at least until August 4th, 2022
077   *
078   * @since May 5th, 2020
079   */
080  VERSION_7_0("v7.0"),
081
082  /**
083   * <tt>Graph API 8.0</tt>, available at least until November 10th, 2022
084   *
085   * @since August 4th, 2020
086   */
087  VERSION_8_0("v8.0"),
088
089  /**
090   * <tt>Graph API 9.0</tt>, available at least until November 2022
091   *
092   * @since November 10th, 2020
093   */
094  VERSION_9_0("v9.0"),
095
096  /**
097   * convenience enum to provide simple access to the latest supported Graph API Version.
098   * <p>
099   * the current version is <tt>Graph API 9.0</tt>
100   * </p>
101   */
102  LATEST("v9.0");
103
104  private final String urlElement;
105
106  Version(String urlElement) {
107    this.urlElement = urlElement;
108  }
109
110  public String getUrlElement() {
111    return this.urlElement;
112  }
113
114  public boolean isUrlElementRequired() {
115    return null != this.urlElement;
116  }
117
118  /**
119   * converts a String (for example the url parameter) into a Version object
120   * 
121   * @param urlElementStr
122   *          String that should
123   * @return the generated version
124   */
125  public static Version getVersionFromString(String urlElementStr) {
126    if (urlElementStr != null) {
127      return Stream.of(Version.values()).filter(v -> urlElementStr.equals(v.getUrlElement())).findFirst()
128              .orElse(UNVERSIONED);
129    }
130
131    return UNVERSIONED;
132  }
133}
